---
title: Caribbean Coconut & Kidney Bean Curry with Garlic Rice, Charred Pineapple Salsa & Mint
description: Red kidney beans are the star of this vegetarian main course. they're packed with fibre and protein, ideal to turn this mildly spiced chilli into a hearty dinner, while garlic rice and a zesty salsa add oodles of flavour.

